OL,3,CAntisocial behaviour victims can
OL,4,Cdemand policing review in 'UK first'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FRachel Bullock speaks to people
OL,8,Faffected by antisocial behaviour at
OL,9,Fthe scheme's launch
OL,11,FVictims of anti-social behaviour will
OL,12,Fbe able to demand an independent
OL,13,Freview if they are not satisfied with
OL,14,Fhow officers have responded under a
OL,15,Fnew scheme.
OL,17,FPeople living within the area covered
OL,18,Fby Durham Police will be able to
OL,19,Frequest a review if they have reported
OL,20,Fthree or more instances of anti-social
OL,21,Fbehaviour but the offences continue.
