OL,7,FIt is considered the first scheme of
OL,8,Fits kind in the country.
OL,10,FJohn McGee knows more than most about
OL,11,Fthe issue, having said it made him
OL,12,Ffeel nervous to be in his own home.
OL,14,F"There were pitch battles out on the
OL,15,Fstreet," he told ITV News.
OL,17,F"24 hours, seven days a week. Young
OL,18,Fkids coming in and out, up and down
OL,19,Fthe path, smashing doors.
