OL,7,F"Rubbish getting thrown out, round the
OL,8,Fback of the house attracting rats. It
OL,9,Fwas just total mayhem.
OL,11,F"You started to feel like nobody was
OL,12,Fpaying any attention to you."
OL,14,FIt is stories like Mr McGee's that
OL,15,Fhave inspired Durham Police to act,
OL,16,Fwith Police and Crime Commissioner Joy
OL,17,FAllen launching the scheme on Tuesday.
