OL,7,FA more proactive approach has already
OL,8,Fbeen seen in Durham city centre after
OL,9,Fanti-social behaviour plagued the
OL,10,Fmarket hall last September.
OL,12,F"It is nowhere near what it used to
OL,13,Fbe," said Susan Platten, from Brew and
OL,14,FBean.
OL,16,F"The police are doing I really good
OL,17,Fjob I think - if we do have a problem,
OL,18,Fwe give them a ring and honestly they
OL,19,Fare straight in."
