OL,7,FDurham Police has stressed that the
OL,8,Fscheme is designed to help assess
OL,9,Findividual needs rather than push anti-
OL,10,Fsocial behaviour into other areas.
OL,12,FMr McGee believes it will help tackle
OL,13,Fthe issue, adding: "People were
OL,14,Fstarting to say we are going to move
OL,15,Fout, but I said if you move out you
OL,16,Fare going to find somewhere where you
OL,17,Fhave the same happening again.
OL,19,F"I do think people will start taking
OL,20,Fthings seriously now."
